overview: Take a peek inside the hidden face of Zhoom. Over two hours in the intimacy of the candidates in the margins of the shooting of the show. Eleven X-rated scenes in which you will see Tybo Calter, Florian Ladicat, John Despe, Lucas Darren, Dany Benoit, Marvyn Orian, Sébastien Bonnet and the winner of gay reality TV show Zhoom: Adrien Alleg.
title: The Other Side of Zhoom
